metadata.name: Grosso (RIPped) Eggplant, Upland COMBI!! #1/10
metadata.description: The painting is 30”x40” was done with oil paint over spray-can painted background. It was a painting for Eddie Elguera’s classic art show, a tribute to the Combi bowl! This was a tribute to Jeff Grosso, who was one of my favorite all-time skaters, which I’m one of millions! Photo by JGrant brittan.
